'''Justice Mir Khuda Bakhsh Marri''' ({{lang-ur|خدابخش مری}}) was the [[Governor of Balochistan, Pakistan]] from 5 July 1977 – 18 September 1978.<ref>{{cite book|author=Syed Farooq Hasnat|title=Global Security Watch-Pakistan|publisher=ABC-CLIO|year=2011|page=89}}</ref> He was appointed as Chief Justice of Sindh and Balochistan, Pakistan in 1976. He also served as acting Chief Minister of Balochistan in 1989.

